                <h1>Mastering RGB: The Ultimate Guide to Color in Digital Media</h1>
                <p>RGB stands for Red, Green, Blue, and it's a color model used in digital displays to create vibrant images. By adjusting the intensity of these three primary colors, a vast spectrum of colors is produced. Often used in screens, lighting, and design, RGB is essential for visual media in technology.</p>
